      "review_summary": "The PR changes Copilot plugin registration to make `runtime.state.openSyncKeyedStore` optional and omit `sessionStore` when that API is absent.\n\nPR surface: Source +4. Total +4 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main's CLI metadata loader can pass `runtime: {}` while the Copilot entrypoint dereferences `api.runtime.state.openSyncKeyedStore`. I did not execute the reporter-equivalent installed CLI path in this read-only review.",
